result.execSummary:
The defendant Misael O Echevarria Rodriguez was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Misael O Echevarria Rodriguez is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Misael O Echevarria Rodriguez was found guilty of Child Abuse-Intentionally Cause Harm, a class H felony, Wisconsin Statutes 948.03(2)(b).
